[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0021","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0021.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0307","title":"HP HP-UX cstm 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 cstm（Customer Services Test Manager）程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该程序提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，进而覆盖内存中的关键数据，实现权限提升并获得 root 超级用户权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，攻击者需要具有目标系统的本地访问权限，但无需其他特殊条件，利用难度较低，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0307"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-12-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:07.113","remediation":"立即移除 cstm 程序的 setuid root 权限位：`chmod u-s /opt/sfm/bin/cstm`，仅允许受信任的管理员通过 sudo 执行。如业务允许，可彻底卸载 cstm 软件包：`swremove SFM-CSTM`。若系统仍在运行关键业务无法直接卸载，应使用文件权限 ACL 限制 cstm 的执行用户为 root 组，命令：`chmod 750 /opt/sfm/bin/cstm && chown root:sys /opt/sfm/bin/cstm`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0307"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0021.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0020","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0020.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0289","title":"Apache HTTP Server Win32 附加点号致信息泄露漏洞","description":"Apache Web Server for Win32 存在文件访问控制绕过漏洞。当攻击者在请求 URL 末尾附加一个点号（.）时，服务器可能绕过正常权限检查，导致受限制文件被未授权访问。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞读取目标系统中的敏感文件（如配置文件、密码文件等），造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Apache for Win32 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0289"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.840","remediation":"升级到 Apache 1.3.12 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 1.3.x 后续版本中修复。如无法升级，在 Apache 配置中使用 `RewriteRule` 或 `AliasMatch` 拒绝所有以 `.` 结尾的 URL 请求，或在 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）层面过滤 URL 末尾的 `.` 字符作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0289","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0289","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0289.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/openbmc/openbmc/blob/798e84e356727c60a18eb3d0b86fb61b9862fb74/upstream-layers/meta-openembedded/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w6fh-wrw4-q6vg/GHSA-w6fh-wrw4-q6vg.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/Xilinx/meta-openembedded/blob/4d3e2639dec542b58708244662d5ce36810fc510/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.66.bb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0020.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0019","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0019.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0287","title":"WebCom datakommunikation Guestbook rguest.exe 任意文件访问漏洞","description":"WebCom datakommunikation Guestbook 0.1 的 rguest.exe CGI 程序存在任意文件访问漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向该 CGI 程序发送特制请求，利用路径遍历技术读取 Web 服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Guestbook 0.1 版本，攻击条件低、利用简单，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0287"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.593","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器 CGI 目录中删除或重命名 rguest.exe 和 wguest.exe 文件，彻底禁用该留言本组件。在 IIS 中可通过「应用程序配置」移除该脚本映射，或在文件系统层面撤销 IUSR_MACHINENAME 账户对 CGI 目录的执行权限。建议替换为其他仍在维护的开源留言本或使用无文件写入的第三方评论服务（如 Disqus）以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92368828704896&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0287","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0287.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0019.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0018","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0261","title":"NetManage Chameleon SMTPd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NetManage Chameleon SMTPd 服务存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞，源于对 HELO 和 HELP 等 SMTP 命令输入长度缺乏有效边界检查。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 SMTP 端口发送超长命令（如 HELO 后跟超过 471 字符的主机名），触发缓冲区溢出导致服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上的 Chameleon 4.5 及 UnixLink 97 版本，CVSS v2 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0261"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.477","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Netmanage Chameleon 4.5 及 Unixlink 97 的 SMTPd 服务（Windows NT 平台），由于产品早已停止维护且厂商未发布补丁，建议升级迁移至受支持的 SMTP 服务器（如 Exchange Server、Postfix 等）。若暂时无法迁移，应在防火墙限制对 TCP 25 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接；同时监控 SMTP 服务的异常崩溃日志以及时发现攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.insecure.org/sploits/netmanage.chameleon.overflows.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0261","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0261.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9v5m-hg7x-6gfx/GHSA-9v5m-hg7x-6gfx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2387/info.html","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0017","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0017.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0229","title":"Microsoft Windows NT IIS 目录遍历拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 服务器存在路径遍历拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送包含特殊构造的 `..\\..` 序列的 HTTP 请求触发目录遍历，导致服务器资源耗尽或崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统上的 Microsoft IIS 服务，利用方式简单，危害性较高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0229"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.530","remediation":"升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本（含 IIS 5.0+），或在 Windows NT 4.0 上安装 IIS 4.0 Service Pack 及 MS98-004 安全补丁。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中禁用未使用的虚拟目录并移除可执行权限以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0229","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0229","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0229.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79m3-vm8c-387r/GHSA-79m3-vm8c-387r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/iis_crash.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2218/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0229.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0017.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0015","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0015.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0003","title":"Common Desktop Environment ToolTalk RPC 服务缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"ToolTalk 数据库服务器（rpc.ttdbserverd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统发送特制请求即可触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Xi Graphics Maximum CDE 1.2.3、TriTeal TED CDE 4.3 及 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 等系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，属于当年最具破坏力的远程代码执行漏洞之一。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0003"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.353","remediation":"立即禁用 rpc.ttdbserverd 服务（进程名：rpc.ttdbserverd），执行 /usr/bin/killall rpc.ttdbserverd 终止进程，并从 /etc/inetd.conf（或 /etc/xinetd.d/）中注释 rstatd/rusersd 相关行后重启 inetd。对于 SGI IRIX，应安装 SGI 安全公告 19981101-01 中提供的补丁。对于 Sun Solaris 系统，应用 Sun 提供的对应安全补丁（如 SunOS 5.5.1 相关补丁）。上述操作系统均已终止安全支持，强烈建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/122","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19102","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0003.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0003","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/572.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0003.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/rpc.rules","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-gxwg-52wj-vc7w/GHSA-gxwg-52wj-vc7w.json","https://github.com/FIRSTdotorg/Vuln4Cast/blob/c93910d268aa5b5d2260adb9b5d92094b2d06daf/YearlyVuln4Cast-V1.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0014","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0224","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Messenger Service 长用户名拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Messenger 服务在解析超长用户名时存在边界处理缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的超长用户名数据包，触发服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击者无需复杂工具即可通过标准网络协议发包实施攻击，影响 Windows NT 4.0 全版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0224"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.923","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 4.0 的 Service Pack 5 (SP5) 或更高版本，该补丁修复了 Messenger Service 对畸形用户名处理不当的问题。对于已停止支持的旧系统，建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本；若无法升级，可在服务管理器中禁用 \"Messenger\" 服务以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0224","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/329","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0224.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0224","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0224.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0013","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0013.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0223","title":"Sun Solaris syslogd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统 syslogd 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，当远程主机向目标 Solaris 系统发送 syslog 消息时，若该主机缺少反向 DNS（PTR）记录，syslogd 在处理过程中会发生崩溃，导致系统日志服务中断。攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞，持续发送此类消息可使 syslogd 反复崩溃，影响系统日志记录功能。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0223"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.797","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至包含此补丁的版本（如 Solaris 2.6 及以上），或在 /etc/syslog.conf 中禁用反向 DNS 解析功能；同时建议在防火墙层面限制外部主机向 UDP 514 端口发送 syslog 消息，防止未授权来源触发崩溃。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.Sun.COM/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?patchid=103291&collection=fpatches","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1878"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0013.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0012","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0222","title":"Cisco IOS Web Server 长URL拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 路由器的 Web 服务器组件存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标设备发送超长 URL 即可触发缓冲区溢出，导致 IOS 进程崩溃并迫使路由器重新启动，造成网络服务中断。该漏洞影响启用 HTTP 服务的 Cisco IOS 设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。缓解措施为禁用不必要的 HTTP 服务或通过访问控制列表限制来源 IP。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0222"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.680","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至修复版本（如 11.2(18)、12.0(11) 及以上），或禁用 HTTP 服务：全局配置模式下执行 `no ip http server`。如需保留 HTTP 服务，通过 `ip http access-class` 配合 ACL 限制可信管理源地址，并在接口上应用 `ip access-group` 过滤对 80 端口的非授权访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/60159","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0222","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0222.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8cfdaab2997679f3e193ea9539f778b75d8c9d41/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0012.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0012.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0012.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0011","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0221","title":"Lucent Ascend 路由器远程管理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lucent Ascend 路由器远程管理服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标路由器的 150 端口（远程管理端口）发送特制数据包，导致路由器服务崩溃或无法响应正常请求。该漏洞影响 Lucent Ascend 系列路由器，无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级中危。官方已发布固件更新修复此漏洞，建议用户升级至最新版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0221"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.547","remediation":"在防火墙或访问控制列表（ACL）中限制对 TCP/UDP 150 端口的访问，仅允许 trusted 管理 IP 连接。如无需远程管理功能，建议在路由器配置中禁用远程管理服务（no remote-management）。若设备仍在使用，应升级至供应商支持的最新固件版本，或替换为受支持的现代路由器设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0221","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0221.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0221","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-635x-qr4g-qqp3/GHSA-635x-qr4g-qqp3.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80896/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0009","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0009.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0199","title":"GNU glibc 未加检查的返回值漏洞","description":"GNU C 库（glibc）2.2 之前版本的 tdelete 函数在删除树根节点时未明确说明返回值类型，导致开发者无法正确判断操作结果，从而可能访问悬空指针。攻击者可利用此缺陷绕过安全检查或触发程序崩溃，影响所有依赖 glibc 的 Linux 系统及应用。该漏洞源于对返回值未加检查（CWE-252），CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0199"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2020-10-06T13:15:13.087","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.723","remediation":"升级 GNU C Library (glibc) 至 2.2 及以上版本，该版本已明确定义 tdelete 函数在删除树根节点时的返回值。开发者应在调用 tdelete 后始终检查返回值是否为 NULL，避免使用悬空指针。无法立即升级的应用可通过静态代码扫描工具（如 cppcheck）检测 tdelete 返回值未检查的模式。临时缓解措施可结合内存安全防护机制（如 AddressSanitizer）在开发阶段捕获此类缺陷。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/glibc/glibc-2.2.tar.gz","https://github.com/bminor/glibc/commit/2864e767053317538feafa815046fff89e5a16be#diff-94e8c502f255fdfc346df0e29fd4ef40","https://www.cee.studio/tdelete.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0009.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0007","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0194","title":"UNIX in.comsat 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"in.comsat（Unix 邮件通知服务）存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标主机的 comsat 服务（UDP 512 端口）发送特制的伪造消息数据包，触发服务生成大量告警通知并消耗系统资源，导致目标主机拒绝服务。受影响的系统包括各类 Unix 衍生系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等问题。厂商已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0194"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.103","remediation":"在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释或删除 comsat 行并重启 inetd 服务以禁用该服务；或在防火墙上封禁外部对 UDP 512 端口的访问。如需保留功能，请升级操作系统至厂商已发布修复补丁的最新版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0194"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0005","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0002","title":"Caldera OpenLinux NFS mountd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NFS 服务中的 mountd 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获得 root 权限，实现完全控制目标系统。该漏洞主要影响 RedHat Linux 5.1、Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 等 Linux 发行版，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0002"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-10-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.113","remediation":"立即升级 NFS mountd 相关软件包。Red Hat Linux 用户应升级至 5.2 及以上版本；Caldera OpenLinux 用户应升级至 Standard 1.3 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上封锁 NFS 相关端口（如 TCP/UDP 111、2049），或直接禁用 NFS 服务（`/etc/init.d/nfs stop`）及 rpc.mountd 守护进程。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-006.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/121","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19096"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0004","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0140","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 RAS/PPTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 3.51 及 NT 4.0 的远程访问服务（RAS）与 PPTP 协议实现中存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形控制数据包，可导致 RAS/PPTP 服务崩溃或停止响应，造成系统无法正常提供远程访问功能。该漏洞无需用户交互即可远程触发，影响范围涉及企业远程接入环境，可能导致业务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0140"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.957","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 或更高版本以修复 RAS/PPTP 协议处理中的缺陷。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022），并在防火墙上限制对 PPTP 端口（TCP 1723）的访问以降低暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20508","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0140","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0140.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fg49-hp4g-2h7r/GHSA-fg49-hp4g-2h7r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/winnt_pptp_dos.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0003","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0002","title":"Linux NFS mountd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NFS mountd 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获取受影响系统的 root 权限。该漏洞主要影响 Linux 系统，包括 RedHat Linux 5.1 及 Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 等版本。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，建议立即升级至修复版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0002"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-10-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.113","remediation":"RedHat Linux 5.1 用户应升级至 RedHat Linux 5.2 或安装对应安全补丁；Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 用户需更新至修复版本；SGI 系统应安装公告 19981006-01-I 提供的补丁。在不影响业务的前提下，可禁用 NFS 服务（/etc/init.d/nfs stop）或使用 tcpwrappers（/etc/hosts.allow）限制对 rpc.mountd 的访问来源，同时通过防火墙仅允许可信 IP 访问 RPC 端口（111/TCP/UDP）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-006.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/121","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19096","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0002.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0002.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0002","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0002.json","https://github.com/demisto/content/blob/710308a4be78e89bc993b4d594b444aeb805b7d8/Packs/IntSight/Integrations/Rapid7ThreatCommand/README.md","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0002.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-222m-mgc9-9mqv/GHSA-222m-mgc9-9mqv.json","https://github.com/MAECProject/python-maec/blob/13e66105c9646156060d0896a4d54970ea358f44/maec/bindings/maec_bundle.py","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/FIRSTdotorg/Vuln4Cast/blob/c93910d268aa5b5d2260adb9b5d92094b2d06daf/YearlyVuln4Cast-V1.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0003.toml"}]